data.name: welcome_email
data.subject: Welcome to RemoteHive!
data.html_content:
Welcome to RemoteHive!

Dear {{user_name}},

Thank you for joining our platform. Start exploring remote opportunities today!

Best regards,
The RemoteHive Team
data.text_content: Welcome to RemoteHive! Dear {{user_name}}, Thank you for joining our platform. Start exploring remote opportunities today! Best regards, The RemoteHive Team

data.name: job_alert
data.subject: New Jobs Matching Your Preferences
data.html_content:
New Job Opportunities

Hi {{user_name}},

We found {{job_count}} new jobs that match your preferences:

    {% for job in jobs %}
  • {{job.title}} at {{job.company}} - {{job.location}}
    • {% endfor %}

View All Jobs
data.text_content: Hi {{user_name}}, We found {{job_count}} new jobs that match your preferences. Visit {{base_url}}/jobs to view them.

data.name: email_verification
data.subject: Verify Your Email Address
data.html_content:
Email Verification

Hi {{user_name}},

Please click the link below to verify your email address:

Verify Email

If you didn't create an account, please ignore this email.
data.text_content: Hi {{user_name}}, Please visit {{verification_url}} to verify your email address. If you didn't create an account, please ignore this email.

data.name: application_status
data.subject: Application Status Update
data.html_content:
Application Status Update

Hi {{user_name}},

Your application for {{job_title}} at {{company_name}} has been {{status}}.

{% if status == 'accepted' %}

Congratulations! The employer will contact you soon.

{% elif status == 'rejected' %}

Thank you for your interest. Keep applying to other opportunities!

{% endif %}

View Your Applications
data.text_content: Hi {{user_name}}, Your application for {{job_title}} at {{company_name}} has been {{status}}. Visit {{base_url}}/applications to view your applications.

data.name: support_request
data.subject: Support Request Received
data.html_content:
Support Request Received

Hi {{user_name}},

We've received your support request and will get back to you within 24 hours.

Request Details:

Subject: {{request_subject}}

Message: {{request_message}}

Reference ID: {{ticket_id}}
data.text_content: Hi {{user_name}}, We've received your support request and will get back to you within 24 hours. Reference ID: {{ticket_id}}
